drunks are helpless victims of an uncontrollable disease which she 
said has encouraged some judges to give light sentences for drunken 
driving 
i feel this decision is fair and just and that this encourages 
judges to give sentences to fit the crime of drunken driving she 
said the fundamental issue is responsibility 
