two lesserknown olympic hopefuls by removing the fiveyear waiting 
period permanent residents are required to go through 
rep romano l mazzoli dky the panels chairman who 
regularly opposes olympic bills said he was sympathetic to 
arguments that preventing lendl from participating in the olympics 
would be a true hardship because an athletes prime years are 
limited 
