radiological procedures the spokesman said in a statement 
reagan will undergo a routine series of dental xrays in the 
dental clinic while mrs reagan will have her first postoperative 
mammogram the spokesman said 
fitzwater said the tests represent routine checkups and are 
not associated with any current physical findings or problems 
mrs reagan had her left breast removed on oct 17 1987 after 
doctors discovered a quarterinch cancerous lesion 
