couple expected to be at the medical center in suburban washington 
for about an hour 
its mrs reagans sixmonth checkup and the president 
planned to use the time to get his dental xrays taken rather than 
usually doing it at the white house the spokeswoman said 
mrs crispen said the couple wanted to have the results of mrs 
reagans exam before they left so they could send her off for a 
comfortable worryfree weekend 
the spokeswoman said white house physician dr john hutton 
