aboard trains on western military reservations the sources said 
the subcommittee decisions if they are eventually affirmed by 
the entire armed services committee and then the full senate will 
set up another fight with the house 
although both chambers are controlled by democrats reagans 
defense budget requests have generally fared better in the more 
conservative senate and thursdays votes continued that trend 
the defense bills which separately pass each chamber will 
eventually go to a housesenate conference committee to iron out 
differences 
