600000 fines were based on the amount of money the companies made 
during the commissions monitoring process 
in an 11month period atampt received 55 million from calls 
made to one audio enterprises inc line patrick said of that 
amount audio enterprises received 650000 he said intercambio 
inc received 297000 from its operation 
the decision was the result of an fcc investigation triggered by 
complaints alleging that unimpeded access to the sexually explicit 
messages resulted in the molestation of one 10yearold girl and so 
disturbed a 16yearold boy that he had to enter weekly psychiatric 
theraphy 
the companies have 30 days to pay or seek reduction of the fines 
current fcc regulations direct the dialaporn companies to 
restrict their messages through access codes message scrambling or 
use of credit card numbers 
